Trade/Device Name(s): TysonBio MD100 Blood Glucose Monitoring System
TysonBio MD100 Pro Blood Glucose Monitoring System
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): TysonBio MD100 Pro Blood Glucose Meter
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for TysonBio MD100 and MD100 Pro Blood Glucose Monitoring System for quantitative measurement of glucose in capillary and venous whole blood samples
Indications for Use Summary: For quantitative measurement of glucose in capillary and venous whole blood samples as an aid to monitor effectiveness of diabetes control; MD100 for self-testing at home, MD100 Pro for multiple-patient use in professional healthcare settings; not for diagnosis, screening, or neonatal use.
